latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I hope someone out there has this email 😂

Check out my convo with @nhl Hall of Famer Keith Tkachuk on this weeks episode of @youthinc pres. by @invisalign

Check out our latest episode of @youthinc @invisalign w/ special guest @thecoopermanning!

We covered everything from college recruiting to flashback stories of Peyton and Cooper playing together in HS!

Enjoy!
Some thoughts on @youthinc and why this conversation is resonating with so many people across the country.

“Because if you love it, your going to work hard at it”

🚨Episode 3 of @youthinc pres. by @invisalign has dropped!

Had the pleasure of speaking with Olympic Gold medalist @shawnjohnson about her journey as a young athlete and her perspective on youth sports now as a mother!
#ad @ReadyRefresh delivers healthy hydration to your door.

Even though we only played one season together in Carolina, it was easy to see @brianburns99 was working towards something greater than just football. The company that you and your brother started for athletes is truly special. @PlayersTribune @Truist

TJ felt so proud to be asked to be the “Keep Pounding” drummer at Sundays @panthers game!

TJ represents ALL of the patients whose lives have been saved by @levinechildrens! It has never been about TJ and our family, but rather all of the families this special place serves. 

It was made even more special to share the day with @gonzalo.wallis. Dr Wallis has been by our side during this entire journey and we will never be able to repay him or his incredible team!

Our work through @the_heartest_yard is just getting started. We look forward to sharing our plans in the future!

#halveaheart 

#haveaheart💚

❤️ Today will be a special Day! 💚

#keeppounding

When the weather gets colder, skin gets dry and chapped but soft hands are essential for catching passes! Well... not for me anymore 😂 but I still use Vaseline Men's to help lock in moisture and keep my skin hydration game on point in the winter. It absorbs in seconds allowing me to get back in the booth or out on the field with the fam. Share your skin story with #MySkinSpeaks. #VaselinePartner @vaselinebrand

#GivingTuesday 

Donate $10 or more TODAY (www.r4r.org) and be entered to win our @Panthers ❎ @LevineChildrens beanie by @NewEraCap!

We will randomly select 5 winners! 

Beanies go on sale to the public this month! @levinechildrens @the_heartest_yard ❤️💚

So much fun with @Chicken1of1 hunting for rookie cards on @thumbprintbreaks. 

My signed rookie card and 2005 Tom Brady card pulled by me is listed on @pristineauction

100% of the proceeds from both will support my foundations, Receptions for Research (r4r) and @the_heartest_yard.

See the full video @thumbprintbreaks and link in my bio to r4r.
